    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# TF-IDF vs Embeddings Benchmark\\n\",\"**NLP Project 15 of 100**\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Project Overview\\n\",\"Compare classic TF-IDF features against dense word embeddings for text classification. Benchmark both speed and quality.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Implement TF-IDF and sentence embedding pipelines.\\n\",\"2. Compare performance on classification tasks.\\n\",\"3. Measure training/inference time.\\n\",\"4. Understand when each approach wins.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in [\\\"pandas\\\",\\\"numpy\\\",\\\"matplotlib\\\",\\\"seaborn\\\",\\\"scikit-learn\\\",\\\"datasets\\\",\\\"sentence-transformers\\\"]:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg.replace('-','_'))\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"pip\\\",\\\"install\\\",\\\"-q\\\",pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns, time\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\\nfrom sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score\\nfrom sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\\nSEED = 42; np.random.seed(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from datasets import load_dataset\\nds = load_dataset('imdb', split='train').shuffle(seed=SEED).select(range(3000))\\ndf = ds.to_pandas()\\nX_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df['text'], df['label'], test_size=0.2, random_state=SEED)\\nprint(f'Train: {len(X_train)}, Test: {len(X_test)}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## TF-IDF Pipeline\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"t0 = time.time()\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=10000, ngram_range=(1,2))\\nX_tr_tfidf = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train); X_te_tfidf = tfidf.transform(X_test)\\nlr_tfidf = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000, random_state=SEED)\\nlr_tfidf.fit(X_tr_tfidf, y_train)\\ny_pred_tfidf = lr_tfidf.predict(X_te_tfidf)\\ntfidf_time = time.time() - t0\\nprint(f'TF-IDF: Acc={accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred_tfidf):.4f}, F1={f1_score(y_test,y_pred_tfidf):.4f}, Time={tfidf_time:.1f}s')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Sentence Embeddings Pipeline\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer\\n\\nt0 = time.time()\\nmodel = SentenceTransformer('all-MiniLM-L6-v2')\\nX_tr_emb = model.encode(X_train.tolist(), show_progress_bar=True, batch_size=64)\\nX_te_emb = model.encode(X_test.tolist(), show_progress_bar=False, batch_size=64)\\nlr_emb = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000, random_state=SEED)\\nlr_emb.fit(X_tr_emb, y_train)\\ny_pred_emb = lr_emb.predict(X_te_emb)\\nemb_time = time.time() - t0\\nprint(f'Embeddings: Acc={accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred_emb):.4f}, F1={f1_score(y_test,y_pred_emb):.4f}, Time={emb_time:.1f}s')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Comparison\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"results = pd.DataFrame([\\n    {'Method':'TF-IDF','Accuracy':accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred_tfidf),'F1':f1_score(y_test,y_pred_tfidf),'Time':tfidf_time},\\n    {'Method':'Embeddings','Accuracy':accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred_emb),'F1':f1_score(y_test,y_pred_emb),'Time':emb_time}\\n])\\nprint(results.to_string(index=False))\\n\\nfig, axes = plt.subplots(1,2,figsize=(12,4))\\nresults.plot(x='Method',y=['Accuracy','F1'],kind='bar',ax=axes[0]); axes[0].set_title('Quality'); axes[0].set_ylim(0.75,1.0)\\nresults.plot(x='Method',y='Time',kind='bar',ax=axes[1],color='coral',legend=False); axes[1].set_title('Time (seconds)')\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **TF-IDF is much faster** but captures only surface-level word patterns.\\n\",\"- **Sentence embeddings capture semantic meaning** and handle synonyms better.\\n\",\"- **For short texts, embeddings often win**; for long documents, TF-IDF is competitive.\\n\",\"- **Best practice: benchmark both** and choose based on latency vs quality trade-off.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
